ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: This class is good if you have some modeling background and/or marketing background. Sometimes I feel that we just dive into the papers without providing enough information about why this is important or that it should be studied. There was one class in which Sudhir mapped out the larger picture about where a body of research stands among bigger things, but all in other classes, I almost felt like we were covering small pockets of research areas that were independent and not related.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
